reviewText: I thought the movie was alright. Not the best Asian movie I've ever watched, but not the worst either. The ending is a bit bittersweet....
My favorite asian actor  makes a movie that was so disgusting I don't know. Its free to anyone  that wants it,or I'm selling it to a used movie store.. Did not watch all of it,thats how bad it is.
A good drama, sometimes a little hard to watch though. Good acting.....interesting story! The DVD came very quickly! I would purchase from this seller again!
